name: GIALLOSTYLE (Mario Bava, Argento, Italian Horror from 70's)
description:
Native SD. 1.5 doesn't know what is "mario bava style" or "argento style" so if you trick to mimick the style... good luck with that.

This is a very special embedding to add extra flavour to your compositions. Everything is about colour!

I just wanted to convey the Mario Bava lightning style. It has been trained with the most iconic Mario Bava Movies, Suspiria and Deep Red from Argento.

Yes! there will be a lot of purples, greens and art noveau architecture thrown into your generations! Isn't wonderful?

If you like my embeddings, please consider to support my work in https://ko-fi.com/punkimaster
